<h1>为</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#000099;">wèi</span><span class=alesi>(wei4)</span> , <span style="color:#cc7700;">wéi</span><span class=alesi>(wei2)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciations of 为 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 为</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/do" style="color:black;">do</a>, <a href="/dictionary/handle" style="color:black;">handle</a>, <a href="/dictionary/govern" style="color:black;">govern</a>, act; be</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 4<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 4 strokes: <a href="/character/不" title="bu4: no, not; un-; negative prefix">不</a>, <a href="/character/中" title="zhong1: central; center, middle; in the midst of; hit (target); attain">中</a>, <a href="/character/以" title="yi3: by means of; thereby, therefore; consider as; in order to">以</a>, <a href="/character/方" title="fang1: a square, rectangle; a region; local">方</a>, <a href="/character/天" title="tian1: sky, heaven; god, celestial">天</a>, <a href="/character/分" title="fen1: divide; small unit of time etc.">分</a>, <a href="/character/心" title="xin1: heart; mind, intelligence; soul">心</a>, <a href="/character/开" title="kai1: open; initiate, begin, start">开</a>, <a href="/character/从" title="cong2: from, by, since, whence, through">从</a>, <a href="/character/日" title="ri4: sun; day; daytime">日</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/丶" title="Kangxi radical 3">丶</a>&nbsp;3.3</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 2 <br><small>Other HSK 2 characters: <a href="/character/到" title="dao4: go to, arrive, been to">到</a>, <a href="/character/以" title="yi3: by means of; thereby, therefore; consider as; in order to">以</a>, <a href="/character/要" title="yao4: necessary, essential; necessity">要</a>, <a href="/character/就" title="jiu4: just, simply; to come, go to; to approach, near">就</a>, <a href="/character/可" title="ke3: may, can, -able; possibly">可</a>, <a href="/character/也" title="ye3: also; classical final particle of strong affirmation or identity">也</a>, <a href="/character/得" title="de2: obtain, get, gain, acquire">得</a>, <a href="/character/着" title="zhe: make move, take action">着</a>, <a href="/character/过" title="guo4: pass, pass through, go across">过</a>, <a href="